rows.label: tlk70000019_01_msg0001
rows.name:
All I do is work in the warehouse.
Work, work, work. I never get to do
anything fun.

rows.label: tlk70000019_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I'd really love to do something touristy.
Like go on a shopping spree, or visit
the park in the middle of the city.

rows.label: tlk70000019_01_msg0003
rows.name:
The park was designed by a famous
gardener, did you know that?
It's supposed to be so beautiful...
